Use the standard library
This is how to string_xor of a and b:
  Remember that result is ""
  Remember that i is 0
  Do this a's length times:
    When item i in a is item i in b, then:
      Remember that result is "{result}0"
    But, if not:
      Remember that result is "{result}1"
    End when
    Increase i by 1
  End do
  The answer is result
